data.description: Nestled in Enterprise, this home has more than meets the eye.  Located on a corner lot with ample parking and an oversized attached garage you have room for it all. The spacious living room opens up to the dining room. There is a bonus room for hobbies and games.  Enjoy the fenced corner lot and irrigation well for your green thumb.  See this place today and all it has to offer!
